---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="嚴選茶品 - 88茶葉" description="探索 88茶葉為您精挑細選的台灣高山茶。阿里山、杉林溪、石棹珠露，限時優惠中！">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="products-hero">
    <div class="products-hero-content">
      <span class="section-tag">嚴選茶品</span>
      <h1>2026 春茶大賞<br/>最新採收，限量發售</h1>
      <p>來自台灣四大名山，不妥協的品質承諾。<br/>即日起購買指定春茶，享有【買2送1】老客戶專屬優惠！</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Products List -->
  <section class="products-list-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="products-grid">
        
        <!-- Alishan -->
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/alishan_promo.jpg" alt="阿里山春茶" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="product-badge">熱銷 NO.1</div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <span class="product-category">阿里山茶區 / 1200m+</span>
            <h2>阿里山 頂級春茶</h2>
            <div class="product-desc">
              <p>雲霧繚繞的經典茶區，茶湯蜜綠金黃。這支春茶果膠質特別豐富，帶有阿里山特有的清幽花香，入口極度甘甜柔順，完全不苦澀，是每天喝都不會膩的大眾首選。</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tea-specs">
              <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">發酵度 (輕)</span><div class="spec-dots"><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div></div></div>
              <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">焙火度 (無)</span><div class="spec-dots"><div class="dot active roast"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="brewing-guide"><div class="brew-icon">♨️ 95°C</div><div class="brew-icon">⚖️ 1:50</div><div class="brew-icon">⏱️ 50秒</div></div>
            
            <div class="product-price">
              <span class="price-current">買 2 斤 送 1 斤</span>
              <span class="price-note">共 3 斤 只要 <strong>$2,000</strong></span>
            </div>
            <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/%40wgc0409f" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="product-cta">加 LINE 搶購 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Shanlinxi -->
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/tea-pour.jpg" alt="杉林溪春茶" loading="lazy" style="filter: brightness(0.9);" />
            <div class="product-badge" style="background: var(--tea-green-deep);">行家推薦</div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <span class="product-category">杉林溪茶區 / 1600m+</span>
            <h2>杉林溪 珍藏春茶</h2>
            <div class="product-desc">
              <p>愛喝「冷礦味」的老饕看過來！來自杉林溪高海拔，帶有獨特的冷礦山氣與竹杉香。茶湯清澈，口感厚實、層次豐富，吞下後回甘明顯，喉頭會一直維持甘甜的感覺。</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tea-specs">
              <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">發酵度 (輕)</span><div class="spec-dots"><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div></div></div>
              <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">焙火度 (輕)</span><div class="spec-dots"><div class="dot active roast"></div><div class="dot active roast"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="brewing-guide"><div class="brew-icon">♨️ 95-100°C</div><div class="brew-icon">⚖️ 1:50</div><div class="brew-icon">⏱️ 55秒</div></div>
            
            <div class="product-price">
              <span class="price-current">買 2 斤 送 1 斤</span>
              <span class="price-note">共 3 斤 只要 <strong>$2,000</strong></span>
            </div>
            <p class="mix-note">💡 可選 2斤杉林溪 + 1斤阿里山混搭</p>
            <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/%40wgc0409f" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="product-cta">加 LINE 搶購 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Zhulu -->
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-image">
            <img src="/images/zhulu_promo.jpg" alt="石棹珠露" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="product-badge" style="background: var(--gold-dark);">VIP 隱藏版</div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-info">
            <span class="product-category">石棹茶區 / 頂級生茶</span>
            <h2>阿里山 石棹珠露</h2>
            <div class="product-desc">
              <p>只有老客戶才收到的隱藏版！茶湯擁有極高雅的清香與鮮度，喉韻超級濃郁！一口喝下，回甘的感覺會在嘴裡繞很久，是行家指定的「極致回甘款」，喝過就回不去了。</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tea-specs">
              <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">發酵度 (中輕)</span><div class="spec-dots"><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot active ferment"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div></div></div>
              <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">焙火度 (中)</span><div class="spec-dots"><div class="dot active roast"></div><div class="dot active roast"></div><div class="dot active roast"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="brewing-guide"><div class="brew-icon">♨️ 100°C</div><div class="brew-icon">⚖️ 1:40</div><div class="brew-icon">⏱️ 60秒</div></div>
            
            <div class="product-price">
              <span class="price-current">買 3 斤 送 1 斤 梨山</span>
              <span class="price-note">共 4 斤 只要 <strong>$3,600</strong></span>
            </div>
            <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/%40wgc0409f" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="product-cta">加 LINE 搶購 →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quality Promise -->
  <section class="promise-section">
    <div class="section-inner text-center">
      <h2>為什麼選擇 88茶葉？</h2>
      <div class="promise-wrap">
        <div class="promise-item">
          <h3>📦 免運費 貨到付款</h3>
          <p>買茶無壓力，在家收貨最安心</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-item">
          <h3>💯 不滿意 包退費</h3>
          <p>喝不習慣？我們無條件退換</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-item">
          <h3>👩‍💼 真人客服 專業推薦</h3>
          <p>不會選茶？加 LINE 由專人為您解答</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .products-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 38, 24, 0.7), rgba(26, 38, 24, 0.8)), url('/images/hero-tea.jpg') center/cover;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }
  .products-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  
  .products-list-section {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--parchment-warm);
  }
  .products-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  
  .product-card {
    background: white;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  
  .product-image {
    position: relative;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 350px;
  }
  .product-image img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .product-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--tea-red);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .product-info {
    padding: 3rem 3rem 3rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .product-category {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .product-info h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .product-desc {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  .product-price {
    background: var(--parchment);
    padding: 1.2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .price-current {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--tea-red);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .price-note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .price-note strong {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .mix-note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--tea-green-deep);
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .product-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink) !important;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .product-cta:hover {
    background: var(--gold-dark);
    color: white !important;
  }

  /* Promise */
  .promise-section {
    background: white;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .promise-wrap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
  .promise-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .promise-item p {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .product-image {
      min-height: 250px;
    }
    .product-info {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .product-cta {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
